msItem.title: Old Danish Prayer Book
msItem.note: The following prayers are printed in Middelalderens danske bønnebøger IV :

msItem.title: Prayer to Be Read before the Communion
Prayers to John the Baptist and the Apostles Peter and Andrew
Prayers to Mary Magdalene, St. Catherine of Alexandria, St. Gertrude of Nivelles

collation.p: Fols 112-117, beginning and ending defetively, are now erroneously bound as the last gathering. The text ends on fol. 111v.

condition.p: The manuscript begins defectively and a lacuna occur after fol. 25. Minor damages occur due to wear.

layout.p: Rubrics, initials, explanations etc. in red ink.

physDesc.additions: Provenance notes, personal names etc. are found on fol. 13v, 25r, 38v, 52r and 11r-v.

surrogates.p: Microfilm (master and archive) Neg .832 and Pos. 757 , from 1989. .
